            "title": "PannkaksTårtan",
            "summary": "Contributions: Details: \"Pannkakstårtan,\" a top-down adventure RPG, marked my fourth game project during my time at The Game Assembly. With&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<figure class=\"post__image post__image--right\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://theredtoad.github.io/media/posts/1/as-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"123\" sizes=\"(min-width: 37.5em) 1600px, 80vw\" srcset=\"https://theredtoad.github.io/media/posts/1/responsive/as-2-xs.png 384w ,https://theredtoad.github.io/media/posts/1/responsive/as-2-sm.png 600w ,https://theredtoad.github.io/media/posts/1/responsive/as-2-md.png 768w ,https://theredtoad.github.io/media/posts/1/responsive/as-2-lg.png 1200w ,https://theredtoad.github.io/media/posts/1/responsive/as-2-xl.png 1600w\"></figure>\n<p class=\"align-left\"><strong>                     Contributions:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Player Controller</li>\n<li>Dialogue System</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\n<p>\"Pannkakstårtan,\" a <strong>top-down adventure RPG</strong>, marked my <strong>fourth</strong> <strong>game project</strong> during my time at <strong>The Game Assembly</strong>. With a team of <strong>5 programmers</strong>, <strong>4 artists</strong>, and <strong>2 desig</strong><strong>ners</strong>, we collaborated over the span of <strong>8 weeks</strong>. We used TGE school's own <strong>framework </strong>and <strong>Unity </strong>as our <strong>level editor</strong>.</p>\n<hr>\n<h3><strong>Intro</strong></h3>\n<p> </p>\n<p>As part of my responsibilities, I led the development of the player controller. This included fine-tuning movement and rotation mechanics and setting up a smooth state machine to handle different player actions seamlessly. I also added dynamic animations to make the character's movements feel more natural and responsive. In addition to these main tasks, I pitched in with other features to make sure the gameplay experience was immersive and complete.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
